# 3. bag_put("greeting", "Hello!")   - Store in memory
# 4. bag_search("hi there")          - Semantic search (works now!)
#
# For LLM generation, you need to plug a model first:
#   hub_search("phi-2")              - Find models
#   hub_search_datasets("sentiment") - Find datasets for grounding
#   plug_model("microsoft/phi-2")    - Load into slot
#   generate("Write a poem")         - Now generate() works!
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 🔗 WHAT WORKS NOW vs NEEDS PLUG
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#   WORKS IMMEDIATELY (baked-in embedder):
#     embed_text()    - Get text embeddings
#     bag_search()    - Semantic memory search
#     bag_put()       - Store with auto-embedding
#     forward()       - Run through brain
#     deliberate()    - Council reasoning
#     imagine()       - World model simulation
#     infer()         - Full consensus inference
#
#   NEEDS plug_model() FIRST:
#     generate()      - LLM text generation
#     classify()      - Classification (needs classifier model)
#     chat()          - Conversational LLM
#     agent_chat()    - Tool-using drill-down slot session
#
