# 📖 COMPLETE EXAMPLE - Memory search (no setup needed!)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#   Step 1: bag_put("doc1", "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog")
#           --> Stored with automatic embedding
#
#   Step 2: bag_put("doc2", "Python is a programming language")
#           --> Stored with automatic embedding
#
#   Step 3: bag_search("canine animal")
#           --> Returns "doc1" (semantic match to "dog"!)
